content: I have a Google Pixel 2 XL and I cannot for the life of me figure out how to get these emojis to work. They aren't showing up in my keyboards or my settings, but when I open the app and hit the install button it says "SUCCESS!" I am sad that I cannot give a chef's kiss to the chef's kisses.
These stickers are...what the title says. They wouldn't show up in Samsung keyboard stickers but are delightful when using Gboard.
Amazing. Had a little bug with the latest update that was fixed within a few hours, which means I will be throwing out Guy Fieri chef kisses left and right now! Can't ask for better service.
This app changed my life by culling all the retrospectively toxic relationships that were unwilling to accept my new chef kiss ways.
I'm going to use this emoji a lot. Its perfect!
I cant use it as a sticker.... only as a picture.. might just uninstall
a versatile sticker pack that sparks joy. a perfect compliment to any sentence or emotion. wonderful.
This is the greatest item to ever be offered on this platform.
